      "id": "sybil_13_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies reliability and sophisticated engineering. This unit has been maintained to rigorous standards, ensuring a seamless driving experience for its next owner. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, it offers an exceptional balance of performance and prestige. We invite discerning buyers to appreciate the caliber of this well-preserved specimen.",
