      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound example featuring a high-revving 4.0L flat-six boxer engine mated to a precision six-speed manual transaxle. This unit benefits from a recently serviced limited-slip differential and a factory-tuned PASM suspension system that retains excellent damping characteristics. The chassis remains rigid with crisp turn-in response, and the braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors with multi-piston monobloc calipers for consistent thermal management. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with its mileage, the aerodynamic balance and powertrain mapping remain fully optimized for spirited driving. A driver-focused machine with a clean rev-range history and verified compression across all cylinders.",
